### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nessa Savard",
  "email": "nessa@straycare.com",
  "passwordHash": "password123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###  Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nessa@straycare.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create a dog
POST http://localhost:8080/api/dogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJuZXNzYUBzdHJheWNhcmUuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IkFETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc0NjMxOTE0LCJleHAiOjE3NzQ3MTgzMTR9.xJs6S-5RNDXIcCk3NfOz0__dCKTNffZuL_5mHU4zZfw

{
  "name": "Buddy",
  "breed": "Labrador",
  "status": "active"
}

### Get all dogs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dogs

