### Get all sightings (for heatmap)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sightings

### Submit a sighting with verified field
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sightings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dog": { "id": 1 },
  "latitude": 45.3456,
  "longitude": -75.6789,
  "notes": "Spotted near the park",
  "verified": false
}